This is how to add_elements of arr and k:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this k times:
      When i is at most arr's length, then:
         When item i in arr is less than 100, then:
            Remember that total is sum of total and item i in arr
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
